ðŸ‘‰IN FORM  like (6,7,8,9)ðŸ‘‰ <input type="text" required name="phone_number" pattern="[6-7-8-9]{1}[0-9]{9}" > this is used for 10 digit and starting no. ðŸ‘‰like (6,7,8,9)ðŸ‘ˆ if you want to add more number so edit this num.
